    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on the idea of \"absolute sovereignty\" over speech? Specifically, how would that argument handle the idea that certain types of online content—like hate speech or misinformation—actually harm the democratic process or public safety? I want to make sure my post addresses those counterpoints from a philosophical perspective.",
